# Cursor Plans Git Tracking

## Requirement

The `plans/` folder SHALL be tracked in git. It SHALL NOT be added to `.gitignore`.

## Rationale

Tracking plans in git ensures:
- Full traceability of planning decisions
- Audit trail of development approach
- Historical record of project evolution
- Ability to review past planning approaches
- Recovery of planning context
- Team members can review planning decisions


